                            <comment id="14649654" author="roboduke" created="Thu, 15 Feb 2024 04:43:54 -0800"  >[jdk21u-fix-request] Approval Request from Aleksey Shipil&amp;#xEB;v&lt;br/&gt;
Changes how VTs interact with JVMTI. In mainline since Sep 2023, there is no bug tail. We want this fix to provide the ground for the rest of backports. Notably, it makes &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8312777&quot; title=&quot;notifyJvmtiMount before notifyJvmtiUnmount&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JDK-8312777&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JDK-8312777&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt; backport clean. The fix is part of large atomic change, see 21u PR.</comment>
                            <comment id="14649649" author="roboduke" created="Thu, 15 Feb 2024 04:39:02 -0800"  >A pull request was submitted for review.&lt;br/&gt;
URL: &lt;a href=&quot;https://git.openjdk.org/jdk21u-dev/pull/245&quot;&gt;https://git.openjdk.org/jdk21u-dev/pull/245&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Date: 2024-02-08 11:17:02 +0000</comment>
                            <comment id="14610024" author="alanb" created="Mon, 11 Sep 2023 02:47:46 -0700"  >&amp;gt; Could you please link up the relevant JVMTI change to this bug? &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
The JVMTI work was mostly done in loom repo before the JEP 425 into JDK 19, it&amp;#39;s been refined with several changes since then that include &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8293613&quot; title=&quot;need to properly handle and hide tmp VTMS transitions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JDK-8293613&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JDK-8293613&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8304303&quot; title=&quot;implement VirtualThread class notifyJvmti methods as C2 intrinsics&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JDK-8304303&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JDK-8304303&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8306028&quot; title=&quot;separate ThreadStart/ThreadEnd events posting code in JVMTI VTMS transitions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JDK-8306028&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JDK-8306028&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. So nothing to backport to JDK 21u at this time.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
The main goal here is to avoid having some ops unmounting before freeze but monitorenter freezing before unmounting. It&amp;#39;s impossible to say when everything will be stable for main line but I think everything will need to bake for a time before thinking about back ports.</comment>
                            <comment id="14610015" author="shade" created="Mon, 11 Sep 2023 02:21:01 -0700"  >&amp;gt; JVMTI has since introduced a means to hide events during transitions so the implementation has be reverted&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Could you please link up the relevant JVMTI change to this bug?&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Should this fix be considered for JDK 21?&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
